{"word":"H1272 - בָּרַח - bârach - baw-rakh' - Chase ; drive away","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בָּרַח</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bârach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>baw-rakh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Chase ; drive away"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஒடிப்போ, தப்பி, பறந்து போ, தீவிரி, துரத்து, ஒடிப்போனது. பாய்ச்சப்பட்டிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to go through, to flee, to run away, to chase, to drive away, to put to flight, to reach, to shoot (extend), to hurry away"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to go, to pass through"},{"paragraph":"2) to flee"},{"paragraph":"3) to hasten, to come quickly"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to pass through"},{"paragraph":"2) to cause to flee, to put to flight"},{"paragraph":"3) to drive away"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>bolt</i>, that is, figuratively to <i>flee</i> suddenly: - chase (away); drive away, fain, flee (away), put to flight, make haste, reach, run away, shoot."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1272 - בָּרַח - bârach - baw-rakh'/1272\">H1272</a>, <a href=\"#/H1273 - בַּרְחֻמִי - Barchumîy - bar-khoo-mee'/1273\">H1273</a>, <a href=\"#/H1276 - בֵּרִי - Bêrîy - bay-ree'/1276\">H1276</a>, <a href=\"#/H1280 - בְּרִיחַ - bᵉrîyach - ber-ee'-akh/1280\">H1280</a>, <a href=\"#/H1281 - בָּרִיחַ - bârîyach - baw-ree'-akh/1281\">H1281</a>, <a href=\"#/H1282 - בָּרִיחַ - Bârîyach - baw-ree'-akh/1282\">H1282</a>, <a href=\"#/H4015 - מִבְרָח - mibrâch - mib-rawkh'/4015\">H4015</a>"}]}